flowchart TD
    A[Turn On Mac] --> B[Connect to Wi-Fi]
    B --> C[Sign In with Company Account]
    C --> D[Complete MFA]
    D --> E[Automated Setup Runs]
    E --> F[Connect to Zscaler]
    F --> G{On-site?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Connect to Secure Company Wi-Fi]
    G -- No --> I[Continue on Current Network]
    H --> J[Access Microsoft 365 Apps]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Open Self Service]
    K --> L[Install Approved Apps]
    L --> M[Ready for Work].venv/
